            "title": "Shifting Strategy, Ukraine Goes Toe to Toe With Russia in Bakhmut - The New York Times",
            "published_date": "2023-01-09T13:26:23.000Z",
            "authors": null,
            "description": "Earlier in the war, Ukraine\u2019s leadership was more equivocal about pitched battles with high casualties. There\u2019s no second-guessing this time. Some analysts say it makes sense strategically.",
