            "title": "Supreme Court Evaluates Scope of Attorney-Client Privilege - The New York Times",
            "published_date": "2023-01-09T20:33:56.000Z",
            "authors": null,
            "description": "The justices struggled to decide how to deal with documents that include both legal and business advice.",
